&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Internal Only&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This post is only open to current employees of University Hospitals of Morecambe Bay&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;An exciting secondment opportunity&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; has become available within the Surgical and Critical Care Group. We are seeking a highly driven, committed and compassionate leader to take on secondment role within Trauma &amp; Orthopaedics.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role includes working closely with Clinicians, Team Leaders and the Senior Management Team and multiple providers of healthcare across the primary and secondary care interface. You will provide exceptional management and leadership in both a clinical and operational capacity. You will have an excellent track record in leading groups of staff through change with a shared vision and a common purpose and will have experience of achieving key performance targets.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post will be on a&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt; secondment basis for 12 month &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;and will commence as soon as possible. They will be full time with an expectation of cross bay working at a senior level.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please note if you are shortlisted for interview you will be required to complete a Psychometric Test.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Details will also be emailed to you of a series of Psychometric tests which you should complete in accordance with the timescales specified. These tests will be conducted on-line in advance of your interview with full instructions supplied.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Anyone newly appointed to the trust will be subject to the completion of a satisfactory 6 month probationary period (this includes bank staff). This will give the new staff member an opportunity to become familiar with the role and working environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameCarol ParkJob titleAssociate Director of OperationsEmail addresscarol.park@mbht.nhs.ukTelephone number07977013297Additional contact information&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Informal discussion is very much encouraged, please contact&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Carol Park 07977013297&lt;/p&gt;
